These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, tea
House: wooden, cottage, craftsman
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, train
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, june
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, bird
City: berlin, edinburgh, rome
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, sunflower
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person who growsrose is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the cottage house is the person drinking tea##1
10. the wooden house is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | lemonade   | tea      |
| House          | craftsman      | wooden     | cottage     |
| Transport           | snowmobile | train  | roller   |
| Birthday   | may   | june     | april  |
| Pet   | chinchilla      | ferret      | bird      |
| City   | rome      | edinburgh    | berlin   |
| Flower         | rose    | lily | sunflower |

