.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, april
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, folk
There 3 different types of food: corn, lime, tomato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, mirinda
City: liverpool, hamburg, new-york
 1. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating corn##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Flower         | daisy | bellflower  | begonia     |
| Birthday           | december        | november | april    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | western    | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | jazz    | disco   |
| Food           | tomato        | lime    | corn        |
| Beverage         | soy-milk     | fanta  | mirinda     |
| City     | new-york         | hamburg       | liverpool |

