.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, d&b
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, dunhill
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing, soccer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, superhero
House: cape-cod, cottage, ranch-style
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, camping
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, brown, aquamarine
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of d&b##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre      | d&b   | ambient         | gospel |
| Cigar          | dunhill  | bolivar        | game    |
| Sport           | water-polo | climbing  | soccer  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | documentary | spy         |
| House   | cottage | cape-cod       | ranch-style        |
| Hobby           | card-games       | collecting        | camping       |
| Color     | aquamarine       | light-blue  | brown       |

