.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bus, trike
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, prince, alhambra
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, security-guard
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, snooker
There 3 different types of food: cherry, kale, avocado
City: london, boston, edinburgh
3 different pets are kept: fish, dog, ferret
 1. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 2. the person playing canasta is the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the trike is the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the person eating kale##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the project-manager is the person eating avocado##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| Transport      | trike   | subway        | bus           |
| Cigar         | dunhill | alhambra          | prince      |
| Job           | engineer   | project-manager | security-guard |
| Game   | canasta  | mah-jongg       | snooker         |
| Food   | kale    | avocado          | cherry        |
| City   | boston  | edinburgh        | london     |
| Pet         | fish   | ferret         | dog       |

