There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, yellow, purple
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, russian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, bolivar
 1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the wooden house##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the wooden house##1
 4. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the russian##1
 6. the entrepreneur is the australian##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is the australian##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the lawyer is on the far left##1

