| House          | craftsman      | wooden  | art-deco     |
| Job         | lawyer | chef     | entrepreneur |
| Sport   | basketball  | skiing | ice-hockey     |
| Color   | blue    | purple      | yellow     |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | russian    | australian  |
| Cigar           | dannemann   | bolivar      | baccarat      |

 